description_english: A place where materials can be stored. You can set up which materials are allowed, defaulting to the first one given.
title: BUILD_STOCKPILE

description_english: A building where you can store larvae. They will be kept safe here until you decide to incubate them.
title: BUILD_LARVASTORAGE

description_english: A storage unit that stores energy pods as pure energy. Some buildings require energy to operate. If so, they'll automatically take it from an energy storage within range.
title: BUILD_BATTERYSMALL

description_english: Assign this to a stockpile. Allows an ant to take materials from that stockpile.
title: BUILD_DISPENSER

description_english: An advanced type of dispenser. Pick a material and this dispenser will try to grab it from any suitable stockpile available on the island.
title: BUILD_SMARTDISPENSER

description_english: A building that destroys any material it receives. It can serve as a safeguard to prevent an overflow when stockpiles are full.
title: BUILD_TRASHCAN

description_english: A handy device that can throw materials, enabling ants to put items on a stockpile over a distance.
title: BUILD_CATAPULT_SMALL

description_english: A ballistic device that can throw materials onto a stockpile. Materials can even be thrown to another island. Do bear in mind that it has a limited range. It must be assigned to a target stockpile.
title: BUILD_CATAPULT

description_english: A factory building that uses heat to convert raw scraps into usable ingots.
title: BUILD_SMELTER

description_english: A fabrication machine that can create several different goods.
title: BUILD_WORKSHOP

description_english: An upgraded workshop that is capable of producing goods that require two different types of materials.
title: BUILD_FACILITY

description_english: The largest of the production buildings, it features three inputs to accommodate recipes requiring three distinct ingredients.
title: BUILD_FACTORY

description_english: The largest of the production buildings, it features three inputs to accommodate recipes requiring three distinct ingredients.
title: BUILD_FACTORY

description_english: A heavy factory that grinds down materials into powder forms.
title: BUILD_GRINDER

description_english: A device that looks like a faucet. It can drip acid onto a material to create a solution.
title: BUILD_DISSOLVER

description_english: Generates energy whenever an ant carrying iron passes through it.
title: BUILD_DYNAMO

description_english: A device that uses energy from battery buildings to alter the molecular structure of certain materials. It can turn crystallite into a crystal. It will activate automatically whenever an ant carrying the material is nearby.
title: BUILD_ELECTROLYZERLARGE

description_english: A more compact version of the electrolyzer. It has a decreased electrolyzing rate, but it compensates for this by having a higher contact boost. This device is best used in a consecutive layout.
title: BUILD_ELECTROLYZER

description_english: Synthesizes seeds from plants found in the biome. Works better in a clean environment.
title: BUILD_SEED_MAKER

description_english: Plant a seed in this building and a plant will grow out of it. Use it to create a farm.
title: BUILD_PLANT_POT

description_english: Accepts goods and deconstructs them into their raw components.
title: BUILD_DECONSTRUCTOR

description_english: The heart of your colony. Feed her energy so she can produce larvae.
title: BUILD_QUEEN

description_english: A building where larvae can be grown into small workers.
title: BUILD_INCUBATOR

description_english: A factory building that uses the components of two smaller ants to combine them into a bigger one. Newly created ants will have a replenished lifespan.
title: BUILD_COMBINER

description_english: A factory building that uses the components of two smaller ants to combine them into a bigger one. Newly created ants will have a replenished lifespan.
title: BUILD_COMBINER

description_english: A large building that upgrades ants by combining them with materials. Should be connected to a stockpile by using a dispenser. Newly created ants will have a replenished lifespan.
title: BUILD_ASSEMBLER

description_english: A special device that can enhance a larva by combining it with a material. The process takes a while. It needs to be connected to a stockpile via a dispenser.
title: BUILD_LARVABOOSTER

description_english: Feeds individual ants energy pods to replenish their energy.
title: BUILD_FEEDINGSTATION

description_english: A building that uses ants to split them and create an ant swarm.
title: BUILD_HIVE

description_english: A building that can recycle ants into raw materials. It is advisable to only use ants at the end of their lifespan for this purpose.
title: BUILD_CRUSHER

description_english: A gigantic building that is required to develop a princess into a gyne.
title: BUILD_ROYALPALACE

description_english: Assign this to a landing pad. Ants capable of flight can take off and fly to the landing pad.
title: BUILD_FLIGHT_PAD_LAUNCH

description_english: Flying ants will fly to this if connected to a launch pad.
title: BUILD_FLIGHT_PAD_LAND

description_english: A larger version of the ant launcher that packs more power. Shooting from elevation also helps to achieve greater distances.
title: BUILD_LAUNCHTOWER

description_english: A small lamp to light up the surroundings. Ants within range will move much faster. It requires energy from an energy storage on the same island.
title: BUILD_BEACONSMALL

description_english: A lamp to light up its surroundings. Ants within range will move faster. It requires energy from energy pods to operate.
title: BUILD_BEACONPOLE2

description_english: After building a concrete core, concrete floor tiles can be freely placed in adjacency to this building.
title: BUILD_CONCRETECORE

description_english: Access to concrete allows you to build floor tiles more efficiently.
title: BUILD_FLOORCONCRETE

description_english: A flat surface that you can place other buildings onto. Using floor tiles allows you to build on a grid.
title: BUILD_CONCRETE_FLOOR

description_english: Inventor ants that are stationed here can be fed by other ants.
title: BUILD_INVENTOR_PAD

description_english: A more efficient alternative to the inventor pad. Full inventor ants will start producing inventor points at a steady rate, eliminating the need to manually pop them.
title: BUILD_INVENTOR_FARM

description_english: A large dish that scans for radio signals from other colonies. Without this building, an ant colony is practically invisible to other colonies.
title: BUILD_RADAR_TOWER

description_english: A building that can reveal a new island on the map. Its sensors are tuned to detect a wide variety of plant species.
title: BUILD_RADAR_UPGRADE1

description_english: A building that can reveal a new island on the map. It can pickup on toxic fumes coming from afar.
title: BUILD_RADAR_UPGRADE2

description_english: A scanner that can reveal a new island on the map. It can pickup toxic fumes coming from wastelands rich in glass.
title: BUILD_ISLANDSCANNERPOLLUTED

description_english: A scanner that can reveal a new island on the map. Who knows what kind of island it might find?
title: BUILD_ISLANDSCANNERRANDOM

description_english: A scanner that can reveal a new island on the map. Who knows what kind of island it might find?
title: BUILD_ISLANDSCANNERRANDOM

description_english: A scanner that can reveal a new island on the map. It can feel the vibrations of heavy objects colliding in the distance.
title: BUILD_ISLANDSCANNERANCIENT

description_english: A sculpture that can act as an expression of civilization. Building this monument shows mastery over the art of bridges.
title: BUILD_CONCRETE_MONUMENT

description_english: A building comprised of many brightly blinking lights, which provides insight into the use of light and color when constructed.
title: BUILD_LEDTERMINAL

description_english: A tall pole emitting a bright light, guiding nearby flying drones during the dark hours. The light is produced through a toxic chemical reaction.
title: BUILD_LIGHTHOUSE

description_english: One of the most important buildings in an ant colony where many kinds of ants can be combined to create a large cocoon, resulting in the emergence of a new queen ready to fly out and establish a new colony
title: BUILD_GYNEMAKER

description_english: A high vantage point where a young queen can wait for the next nuptial flight.
title: BUILD_GYNETOWER

description_english: A nondescript small box that lets you spawn any type of material. Don't ask questions about its origin.
title: BUILD_CHEAT_PICKUPS_SPAWNER

description_english: A nondescript large box that lets you spawn any type of ant. This is seen as cheating in many cultures.
title: BUILD_CHEAT_ANT_SPAWNER
